OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry at first
OL,6,Fwith some hazy evening sunshine.
OL,7,FClouding over through the evening and
OL,8,Fovernight with some patchy light rain
OL,9,Fbut some places remaining dry.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FIt will be cloudy to start the
OL,12,Fday with some patchy rain. Turning
OL,13,Fdrier, brighter through the afternoon
OL,14,Fwith some sunny spells at times.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FMainly
OL,17,Fdry with warm sunny intervals
OL,18,Fdeveloping through the afternoons.
OL,19,FBecoming quite breezy on Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
